---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — Organize with Mary"
  description="Affiliate disclosure for Organize with Mary. Learn how we earn commissions and how that affects our recommendations."
>

  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="container--content">

      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <p>
        Organize with Mary (a Lucente project) participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means that some of the links on this website are affiliate links — if you click on one and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.
      </p>

      <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You pay the same price you would have paid without the affiliate link.</li>
        <li>We earn a small percentage of the sale as a commission from the retailer.</li>
        <li>This helps support the free content on this site.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>
      <p>
        We only recommend products that we genuinely believe will help you organize your small space. We do not recommend products solely because they offer a commission. Our editorial opinions are our own and are not influenced by affiliate partnerships.
      </p>

      <p>
        We always disclose affiliate relationships near the top of any blog post that contains affiliate links, and in our footer.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Programs We Participate In</h2>
      <p>
        We may participate in affiliate programs, including retailer, marketplace, and brand partner programs. This list may be updated as partnerships change.
      </p>

      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines, we disclose any material connections between us and the products or services we recommend. Affiliate links constitute a material connection.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or how we select products, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </article>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding-block: var(--s-12); }
  h1 { margin-bottom: var(--s-2); }
  .legal-updated { margin-bottom: var(--s-8); }
  h2 { margin-top: var(--s-10); margin-bottom: var(--s-3); }
  p, ul { margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  li { margin-bottom: var(--s-2); }
</style>
